  "description": "Extracts the biological rhythm of breath from wind instruments and voice. Slow reactivity smooths over pitch wobble and vibrato, focusing on the inhale/exhale cycle. Long memory sustains the measured breath arc. Moderate selectivity targets the fundamental and lower partials. The coupled signal rises and falls with the performer's lungs.",
